query: SELECT ie.id, ie.name, COUNT(mf.id) as photo_count FROM inspection_environments ie LEFT JOIN inspection_items ii ON ie.id = ii.inspection_environment_id LEFT JOIN media_files mf ON ii.id = mf.inspection_item_id GROUP BY ie.id, ie.name ORDER BY photo_count DESC LIMIT 10;
